summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Belvedere Terrace; Unnamed Street; vacated Prospect Street; A.A. Denny's Broadway Addition to the City of Seattle; the Northeast Quarter of Section 7, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; Lake Forest Park Third Addition;p Seelye Addition; the southwest quarter of Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East; and Town of Seattle, as described below and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
